getDrawableDomain

protected Interval getDrawableDomain(Array1D mipmappedDomain)
Subclasses can override this method to return a domain span that's larger than the maximum according to current mipmapped domain associated with the DrawableDataset. This is sometimes necessary depending on how each datapoint is rendered (e.g. barchart requires domain padding to avoid cropping of the end point bars).
